an al-Kurdi]]\n* [[Jarir ibn Abdullah Al Bajali]]\n{{colend}}\n\n===K===\n{{colbegin}}\n* [[Ka'b ibn Malik]]\n* [[Ka'b ibn Zuhair|Ka'b ibn Zuhayr]]\n* [[Khadijah bint Khuwaylid]] (Wife of Muhammad)\n* {{Interlanguage link multi|Khalid ibn al-As|ar|3=\u062e\u0627\u0644\u062f \u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0627\u0635|vertical-align=sup}}\n* [[Khalid ibn al-Waleed]]\n* [[Khalid ibn Sa`id]]\n* [[Kharija bin Huzafa]]\n* [[Khawlah bint Hakim]]\n* [[Khubayb ibn Adiy]]\n* [[Khunais ibn Hudhaifa|Khunays ibn Hudhayfa]]\n* [[Khuzaima ibn Thabit|Khuzayma ibn Thabit]]\n* [[Kinanah ibn Rabi|Kinana ibn Rabi`]]\n* [[Khabbab ibn al-Aratt]]\n* [[Al-Khansa]]\n{{colend}}\n\n===L===\n{{colbegin}}\n* [[Lab\u012bd|Labid ibn Rabi'a]]\n* [[Layla bint al-Minhal]]\n<!-- * [[Leila bint Abi Houthma]] N'existe ni dans la liste en arabe, ni dans la liste en anglais -->\n* [[Lubaba bint al-Harith]]\n* [[Lubaynah]]\n\n===M===\n[[Malak ibn Nuwayra]]\n* [[Malik al-Dar]]<!-- Is he a Sahaba ? -->\n* [[Maria al-Qibtiyya]]. Wife of Muhammad.\n* [[Malik al-Ashtar]]<!-- Is he a Sahaba ? -->\n* [[Maymuna bint al-Harith]]. Wife of Muhammad.\n* [[Mazin bin Ghadooba]]<!-- Double article with \"Miqdad ibn Aswad\" -->\n* [[Miqdad bin Al-Aswad|Miqdad ibn al-Aswad]]<!-- Double article with \"Miqdad ibn Aswad\" -->\n* [[Muaaz ibn Amr|Mu`adh ibn `Amr]]\n* [[Muadh ibn Jabal|Mu`adh ibn Jabal]]\n* [[Muawiyah I]]{{colbegin}}\n* [[Muawwaz ibn Amr|Mu`awwaz ibn `Amr]]\n* [[Muhammad ibn Abi Bakr]]\n* [[Muhammad ibn Maslamah]]\n* [[Munabbih ibn Kamil]]<!-- Really a Sahaba ? -->\n* [[Mus`ab ibn `Umair]]\n*[[Malik bin Huwairith]]\n* [[Al-Muthanna ibn Haritha]]\n{{colend}}\n\n===N===\n{{colbegin}}\n* [[Naila (Calipha)|Na'ila bint al-Farafisa]]\n*\n[[Nauman]]{{Interlanguage link multi|Nabagha al-Ju'adi|ar|3=\u0627\u0644\u0646\u0627\u0628\u063a\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0639\u062f\u064a|vertical-align=sup|lt=|WD=}}\n* [[Najiyah bint al-Walid]]<!-- Check if she's really a sahabiyya -->\n* {{Interlanguage link multi|Nasiba bint a