 Sahaba]]\n*[[Sunni view of the Sahaba#Sahaba in the Qur'an|Sahaba in the Qur'an]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n\n*[https://archive.org/details/HayatusSahabah The lives of the Sahaba, by Muhammad Yusuf Kandhelvi.]\n*{{in lang|ar}} [https://archive.org/details/sahaba-12345 Sahaba, by Muhammad bin Ali Al-Shukani]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:List Of Sahaba}}\n[[Category:Sahabah|*]]\n[[Category:People from Mecca]]\n[[Category:People from Medina]]\n", "text_old": "{{multiple issues|\n{{cleanup reorganize|date=July 2013}}\n{{globalize|date=July 2013}}\n{{Refimprove|date=September 2009}}\n}}\n\n''[[Sahabah|A\u1e63-\u1e63a\u1e25\u0101bah]]'' ({{lang-ar|\u0627\u0644\u0635\u062d\u0627\u0628\u0629}}, \"The Companions\") were the companions of the [[Islamic prophet]] [[Muhammad]] who had seen or met him, believed in him at the time when he was alive and also died as Muslims.\n\n==Alphabetic list of notable ''sahaba''==\n\n===A===\n\n\n* [[Abbad ibn Bishr]]\n* [[Abdullah ibn Ja'far]]\n* [[Abdu'l-Rahman ibn Abu Bakr]]\n* [['Abd al-Rahman ibn 'Awf]]\n* [[Abdullah ibn Abbas]]\n* [[Abd-Allah ibn Abd-Allah ibn Ubayy]]\n* [['Abd Allah ibn 'Amr ibn al-'As]]\n*[[Abu Basir]]\n* [[Abdullah ibn al-Zubayr]]\n<!-- * {{link-interwiki|vertical-align=sup|en=AAbdullah bin al-`Awar|lang=ar|lang_title=\u0627\u0644\u0623\u0639\u0634\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0632\u0646\u064a\u2018 \u0648\u0627\u0633\u0645\u0647 \u0639\u0628\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0639\u0648\u0631}} Not in the Arabic list -->\n* [[Abdullah ibn Amir]]\n* [[Abdullah ibn Hudhafah as-Sahmi]]\n* [[Abdullah ibn Jahsh]]\n* [[Abdullah ibn Masud]]\n* [[Abdullah ibn Suhail]]\n* [['Abd Allah ibn Rawahah]]\n* [[Abdullah ibn Salam]]\n* [[Ab\u016b l-\u1e6cufayl \u02bf\u0100mir b. W\u0101thila al-Kin\u0101n\u012b]]\n* [[Abdullah ibn Umar]]\n* [[Abdullah ibn Umm-Maktum|Abdullah ibn Umm Maktum]]\n* [[Ab\u00eed ibn Hamal]]\n* [[Ab\u00eed ibn Hunay]]\n* {{Interlanguage link multi|Abjr al-Muzni|ar|3=\u0623\u0628\u062c\u0631 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0632\u0646\u064a|WD=|vertical-align=sup}}\n* [[Abu al-Aas ibn al-Rabiah]], son in law of Muhammad.\n* [[Abu Ayyub al-Ansari]]\n* [[\u2018Abbas ibn \u2018Abd al-Muttalib]]\n* [[Abu Bakr|Abu Bakr as-Siddiq]], father-in-law of Muhammad.\n* [[Abu Dardaa]]\n* [[Abu-Dahr|Ab\u00fb Dhar al-Ghif\u00e2r\u00ee]]\n* [[Abu Dujana (Sahabah)|Abu Dujana]]\n* [[Abu Fuhayra]]\n* [[Abu-Hudhayfah ibn Utbah]]\n* [[Abu Hurairah]]\n* [[Abu Jandal ibn Suhayl|Abu Jandal ibn Suhail]]\n* [[Abu Lubaba ibn Abd al-Mundhir]]\n* [[Abu Musa al-Ashari]]\n* [[Abu Sa`id al-Khudri]]\n* [[Abu Salama `Abd Allah ibn `Abd al-Asad]]\n* [[Abu Sufyan ibn al-Harith]]\n* [[Abu Sufyan ibn Harb]]\n* [[Abu Ubaidah ibn al-Jarrah]]\n* {{Interlanguage link multi|Abz\u00e2 al-Khuz\u00e2`\u00ee|ar|3=\u0623\u0628\u0632\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u062e\u0632\u0627\u0639\u064a|WD=|vertical-align=sup}}\n* {{Interlanguage link multi|Adhayna ibn al-H\u00e2rith|ar|3=\u0623\u0630\u064a\u0646\u0629 \u0628\u0646 \u0633\u0644\u0645\u0629 \u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0627\u0631\u062b|WD=|vertical-align=sup}} <!-- Check if he's the same -->\n* [[Adiyy ibn Hatim|Ad\u00ee ibn H\u00e2tim at-T\u00e2\u00ee]]\n* {{Interlanguage link multi|Aflah ibn Ab\u00ee Qays|ar|3=\u0623\u0641\u0644\u062d \u0628\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0642\u0639\u064a\u0633|WD=|vertical-align=sup}}\n* {{Interlanguage link multi|Ahmad ibn Hafs|ar|3=\u0623\u062d\u0645\u062f \u0628\u0646 \u062d\u0641\u0635|WD=|vertical-align=sup}}\n* {{Interlanguage link multi|Ahmar Abu `Usayb|ar|3=\u0623\u062d\u0645\u0631 \u0623\u0628\u0648 \u0639\u0633\u064a\u0628|WD=|vertical-align=sup}}\n* {{Interlanguage link multi|Ahmar ibn Jazi|ar|3=\u0623\u062d\u0645\u0631 \u0628\u0646 \u062c\u0632\u064a|WD=|vertical-align=sup}}<ref>{{cite web|author=\u0623\u062d\u0645\u062f \u0628\u0646 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f \u0628\u0646 \u062d\u0646\u0628\u0644 \u0628\u0646 \u0647\u0644\u0627\u0644 \u0628\u0646 \u0623\u0633\u062f |url=http://