ir]]\n*[[Malik bin Huwairith]]\n* [[Al-Muthanna ibn Haritha]]\n{{colend}}\n\n===N===\n{{colbegin}}\n* [[Naila (Calipha)|Na'ila bint al-Farafisa]]\n*\n[[Nauman]]{{Interlanguage link multi|Nabagha al-Ju'adi|ar|3=\u0627\u0644\u0646\u0627\u0628\u063a\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0639\u062f\u064a|vertical-align=sup|lt=|WD=}}\n* [[Najiyah bint al-Walid]]<!-- Check if she's really a sahabiyya -->\n* {{Interlanguage link multi|Nasiba bint al-Harith|ar|3=\u0646\u0633\u064a\u0628\u0629 \u0628\u0646\u062a \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0627\u0631\u062b|vertical-align=sup|lt=|WD=}}\n* [[Nuaym ibn Masud]]\n* [[Nafi ibn al-Harith]]<!-- Check if he's really a sahaba -->\n* [[Nufay ibn al-Harith]]<!-- Check if he's really a sahaba -->\n* {{Interlanguage link multi|Nusayba bint al-Harith|ar|3=\u0646\u0633\u064a\u0628\u0629 \u0628\u0646\u062a \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0627\u0631\u062b|vertical-align=sup|lt=|WD=}}\n\n===R===\n{{colbegin}}\n* [[Ratan Al Hindi]]\n* [[Rab'ah ibn Umayah]]\n* [[Rabiah ibn Kab]]\n* [[Rabi'ah ibn al-Harith]]\n* [[Ramlah bint Abu Sufyan|Ramlah bint Abi Sufyan]].Wife of Muhammad.\n* [[Rufaida Al-Aslamia]]\n* [[Ruqayyah bint Muhammad]].Daughter of Muhammad.\n* [[Rumaysa bint Milhan]]\n{{colend}}\n\n===S===\n{{colbegin}}\n* [[Sa'sa'a bin Sohan|Sa`sa`a ibn Suhan]]\n* [[Sad Ibn Abi Waqqas|Sa`d ibn Ab\u00ee Waq\u00e2s]]\n* [[Sa`ad ibn ar-Rabi`|Sa`d ibn ar-Rabi`]]<!-- Really a Sahaba ? -->\n* [[Said ibn Jazied]]\n* [[Sa'd ibn Malik|Sa`d ibn Malik]]\n* [[Sa'd ibn Mua'dh|Sa`d ibn Mu`\u00e2dh]]\n* [[Sa'd ibn Ubadah|Sa`d ibn Ubadah]]\n* [[Sabrah ibn Ma'bad|Sabra ibn Ma`bad]]\n* [[Said ibn Aamir al-Jumahi|Sa`\u00eed ibn \u00c2mir al-Jumahi]]\n* [[Said ibn Zayd|Sa`\u00eed ibn Zayd]]?* {{Interlanguage link multi|Safana bint Hatim at-Ta'i|ar|3=\u0633\u0641\u0627\u0646\u0629 \u0628\u0646\u062a \u062d\u0627\u062a\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0627\u0626\u064a|vertical-align=sup}}\n* [[Safiyyah bint \u2018Abd al-Muttalib]]\n* [[Safiyya bint Huyayy]].Wife of Muhammad.\n* [[Safwan ibn Umayya]]\n* [[Salama Abu Hashim]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.almasalik.com/locationPassage.do?locationId=30261&languageId=ar&passageId=5776 |title=\u0627\u0644\u0645\u0633\u0627\u0644\u0643::\u0642\u0628\u0631 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u062d\u0627\u0628\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0644\u064a\u0644 \u0633\u0644\u0645\u0629 \u0623\u0628\u0648 \u0647\u0627\u0634\u0645 |publisher=Almasalik.com |date= |accessdate=2012-10-04}}</ref>\n* [[Salamah ibn al-Akwa|Salama ibn al-Aqwa]]<!-- Check transliteration with a admin -->\n* [[Salim Mawla Abi Hudhayfah]]\n* {{Interlanguage link multi|Salma bint `Amir|ar|3=\u0633\u0644\u0645\u0649 \u0628\u0646\u062a \u0639\u0645\u064a\u0633|vertical-align=sup}}\n* [[Salma bint Umays]]\n* [[Salma Umm-ul-Khair|Salma bint Sakhri ibn `Amir]] (Umm al-Khayr)\n* [[Salman the Persian|Salman al-F\u00e2ris\u00ee]]\n* [[Sahl ibn Sa'd]]\n* [[Sahl ibn Hunaif]]\n* [[Sahla bint Suhail|Sahla bint Suhayl]]\n* [[Salim Al-Rai]]\n* [[Salit bin 'Amr 'Ala bin Hadrami]]\n* {{Interlanguage link multi|Sakhr ibn Wada`a|ar|3=\u0635\u062e\u0631 \u0628\u0646 \u0648\u062f\u0627\u0639\u0629|vertical-align=sup}}\n* {{Interlanguage link multi|Sakhr ibn Wadi`a|ar|3=\u0635\u062e\u0631 \u0628\u0646 \u0648\u0627\u062f\u0639\u0629|vertical-align=sup}}\n* [[Samra ibn Jundab]]\n* {{Interlanguage link multi|Saraqa ibn `Amru|ar|3=\u0633\u0631\u0627\u0642\u0629 \u0628\u0646 \u0639\u0645\u0631\u0648|vertical-align=sup}}\n* [[Sawda bint Zama|Sawda bint Zam`a]].Wife of Muhammad\n* [[Shams ibn Uthman]]<!-- Sahaba ? Not in arabic list -->\n* [[Shadad ibn Aus]]\n* [[Sharhabeel ibn Hasana]]\n* {{Interlanguage link multi|Shayba ibn `Uthman al-Awqas|ar|3=\u0634\u064a\u0628\u0629 \u0628\u0646 \u0639\u062b\u0645\u0627\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0648\u0642\u0635|vertical-align=sup}}\n* [[Al-Shifa bint Abdullah]]\n* [[Sirin (Islamic history)|Sirin bint Sham'un]]\n* [[Suhayb ar-Rumi]]\n* [[Suhayl ibn Amr]]\n* [[Sumayyah bint Khayyat]]\n* [[Suraqa bin Malik]]\n* [[Shuja' ibn Wahab al-Asad]]\n* [[Suwwad ibn qarib]]\n{{cole